snippet.title: Roger's DeeWorks
snippet.description:
Welcome to my life! This channel is about me and some of the thing that fulfill my life. 

I'm a machinist, I own my shop (DeeWorks.ca), I fabricate things and always push the limit of my knowledge. I'm driven by curiosity and don't think I could ever get bored in this world. Friends, cars, machining, project, test, race car, mistake and success.
